summary: I have another theory about what is going to happen in Avengers End Game.  A while ago I got this book which is a guide to the...
caption:
I have another theory about what is going to happen in Avengers End Game.

A while ago I got this book which is a guide to the MCU cosmos according to the Guardians Of The Galaxy and it appears that the Quantum realm discovered by the Pyms is based on the Negative, Neutral and Superflow zones in the comics. Somebody could navigate time by popping into and out of these realms. In the comics Shield builds a high security prison there so that they can store supervillains, assets and things they want to hide outside normal space. But….These areas are the domain of Anihillus (a way bigger threat than Thanos) and The Builders, a robotic species, who some reckon that the Mind stone intelligence was one of these.

Anyway I reckon that activity by the Avengers using the Quantum realm is going to wake up / attract the attention of Anihillus or some composite character based on him.

summary: To The Girl who loves him last | Bucky x Reader.
body:
To The Girl who loves him last | Bucky x Reader.

Summary: Reader leaves a letter, If anything bad happens.

Warning: Angst Angst ANGST.

“Y/n, Don’t go, I’m sure you can stay.”

First, Take care of him.

When he gets nightmares, Please stay by his side.

“I’ll come back Bucky, I can take care of myself.”

Take care of him, Take care of his heart, Because I knew him long enough to know that he’ll do the same for you.

he sighed and kissed your forehead, “I love you.”

“I love you more.”

Tell him how much you love him every single day. Because the day you’re reading this I won’t be the one saying it to him anymore.

I won’t be able to wake up Every morning and see his face. And sleep with his arms around me, Now.. It’s you.

I didn’t plan on anyone to read this, But I knew It was going to happen. Someday.

Bucky ran up to Steve and looked for you. “Hey where’s Y/n?”

Steve looked down and said “She– She didn’t make it Buck, I’m sorry.”

Make sure to make him smile. Everytime you know he feels sad.

And one last thing. Make him forget me, Not completely. Just make him forget me so he won’t feel pain, And when he remembers, remind him that you’re there for him.

Love,

Y/n.

Years later Bucky found Another girl, Which Reminds him of you. After several years of dating, It was their Wedding day.

Before the wedding Tony knocked on her door, He was greeted by The bride’s warm smile.

“I wanted to give you something.” Tony handed her the White envelope, Tony left and closed the door behind him.

She read words that were written on the envelope, It said.

“to the girl who loves him last.”

The End.

Okay, This was crap, Just thought of it and here it is.

summary: Something In Marvel Movies I Spotted
title: Something In Marvel Movies I Spotted
body:
Avengers End Game.

Avengers Age Of Ultron.

In Avengers End Game, Tony is seen in a ship drifting into space.

In Avengers Age Of Ultron, there is a part where Tony is explaining why he was creating Ultron. He explained that they could kick-ass with people on Earth but he said ‘that up there, that’s the end game’. He was referring to any living things in space.

Tony is in Space in Avengers End Game.

I do not know if anyone else has posted something like this. I found this out today. Whether this was on purpose or not it still relates.

I personally believe this was done on purpose.
